sort typ =
 | Arrow of typ * typ
 | All of typ binding . typ
 | Some of typ binding . typ

sort exp =
 | Lam of exp binding * typ . exp
 | Ap of exp * exp
 | Lam_typ of typ binding . exp
 | Ap_typ of exp * typ
 | Pack of typ * exp * (typ binding . typ)
 | Open of exp * typ binding . (exp binding * typ) . exp
